<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="3">和解여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="12b" n="4"> 이틀 이예 快差시오리이다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="13a" n="1">沿邊이오라</sent>
